Former Liverpool star, Mark Lawrenson has predicted outcomes of the Premier League fixtures and FA Cup semi-final ties taking place this weekend. Manchester City will face Liverpool in the FA Cup semi-final tie on Saturday at Wembley Stadium, while Chelsea will clash with Crystal Palace on Sunday. Southampton will host Arsenal in the Premier League on Saturday, and Manchester United will face Norwich City. Providing his predictions, Lawrenson was quoted by BBC Sport as saying: FA Cup:
Man City 1-2 Liverpool
Chelsea 2-0 Crystal Palace EPL:
Tottenham 2-0 Brighton
Man Utd 2-0 Norwich
Southampton 1-1 Arsenal
Watford 1-2 Brentford
Newcastle 2-1 Leicester
West Ham 1-1 Burnley